<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Techathlon</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.6/css/all.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <span id = "navLogo" onclick="window.location = '/'">CW</span>
        <ul class = "navLinks">
            <li id = "cross"></li>
            <li id = "selectedLink"><a href = "#">About</a></li>
            <li><a href = "/techathlon/play">Play</a></li>
            <li><a href = "/techathlon/leaderboard">Leaderboard</a></li>
            <li><a href = "https://discord.gg/uG6pzB9" target="_blank">Discord</a></li>
            <li id = "logoutImg"><img src = "/images/logout.png" onclick = "window.location='/techathlon/logout'"></li>
            <li id = "logoutText"><a href = "/techathlon/logout">Log out</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div id="hamburger">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <section class="hello">
        <div class="info">
            <h1>Welcome,&nbsp;<span><%= username %></span></h1>    
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fugit veniam nostrum totam, suscipit asperiores iure aut consequuntur natus fuga eos necessitatibus earum quam dicta nobis ducimus ad quos libero dolorem!</p>
            <p>The official cryptic hunt hosted by the Code Warriors of DPS Vasant Kunj will begin on X</p>
            <a href="#rules" class="btn">
                How to play<i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
            </a>
            <a href="/techathlon/play" class="btn om">
                Play<i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/bhai.png" alt="girl">
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="rules" id="rules">
        <div class="head">
            <h1>Rules</h1>
            <div class="bruh"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="points">
            <p>The hunt will last for 48 hours from 11:42 PM to 11:42 PM. </p>
            <p>The answers are not case sensitive and can contain 
                special characters.</p>
            <p> A minor typo will result in an incorrect answer, so be doubly 
                sure of what you enter. For example, if the answer is 
                "codewarriors" and you enter "code wariors", it will be 
                considered incorrect.</p>
            <p>Hints will be posted on the <a href="https://discord.gg/uG6pzB9"><span>discord server</span></a>.</p>
            <p>Spamming the admins for hints is frowned upon.</p>
            <p>The use of any unfair means will be dealt with strictly and 
                you shall be permanently disqualified from participating. </p>
            <p>There is no restriction on the number of times you can enter an 
                answer, so feel free to guess, although random answers are 
                highly unlikely to work.</p>
            <p>If you feel you’re stuck at any point it’s best to clear your head 
                and starting thinking from scratch. </p>
            <p>Refer to the learning resources if you are new to cryptic hunts.</p>
            <p>Have fun playing and don't panic.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <script>
        const burger = document.getElementById("hamburger");
        const cross = document.getElementById("cross");
        const nav = document.querySelector(".navLinks");
        const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll(".navLinks li a");

        burger.addEventListener("click",() => {

            nav.classList.add("nav-active");
            navLinks.forEach(function(link,index){
                link.style.opacity = 0;
                link.style.animation = `navLinkFade 0.5s ease forwards ${index/12+0.1}s`;
            });
        });
        cross.addEventListener("click",() => {
            nav.classList.remove("nav-active");
            navLinks.forEach(function(link,index){
                link.style.animation = "";
                link.style.opacity = 1;
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>